  "body": "![Primal Frontier](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1336081/description_51676466-6665-45e8-9ac8-27d2774e0614.png)\n\n## This mod requires **[Geckolib](https://modrinth.com/mod/geckolib)**\nThis project is in a very early stage, expect bugs and incomplete features!</strong></em></span></p>\n\n***\n\n### About Primal Frontier\n\nPrimal Frontier is a mod that aims to add interesting and unique gameplay to the overworld by reviving prehistoric creatures with their own set of abilites and weaknesses. Choose to see them as threats or tame them and utilize their abilities to your advantage!\n\nCurrently this mod only includes 2 creatures, but as the mod grows,\n\nmany others will be added with unique features, purposes and uses.\n\n<span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\"><strong>Watch our recent video to learn how to tame yourself an antlion!</strong></span>\n<iframe width=\"280\" height=\"157\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/oZ_vExPoFTc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Join the <span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/WYBvB6fWXx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">discord</span></a></span> server to stay updated and participate in the development trough suggestions, polls and questions about future updates and progress in developement!</h2><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>Thanks to everyone who support us through their content!</strong></span></h3>\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>Spoiler</summary>\n  <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/DRekrpO7Bfg\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/jXX50kTdF2I\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/agqO6Kc-LjU\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</details>\n\n\n\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><strong>Credits:</strong></span></h1>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Spoiler</summary>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\"><strong>Coders:</strong></span></h3><pre style=\"text-align: center;\">Deemo</pre><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Animators:</strong></span></h3><pre style=\"text-align: center;\">Deemo</pre><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 152, 219);\"><strong>3D Artists:</strong></span></h3><pre style=\"text-align: center;\">Deemo, duoud23, Sr.Mono</pre>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 152, 219);\"><strong>2D Artists:\n</strong></span></h3><pre style=\"text-align: center;\">Allims2009</pre><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p></div>\n\n</details>\n\n",
